PN,34910
SC,0010
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1673184216
OL,6,FAny publicly funded organisation needs
OL,7,Fto keep on striving to be as efficient
OL,8,Fas possible to give the maximum value
OL,9,Fto those who foot the bill.
OL,11,FBut it still needs proper funding to
OL,12,Fbegin with. It's time to pay up if you
OL,13,Fwant the BBC which is the envy of the
OL,14,Fworld.
OL,3,CStriving to be all things to all people
OL,4,Cnot possible with current BBC funding
